  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "N\u1EBFu ch\xFAng ta ch\u1EC9 nu\xF4i hi v\u1ECDng v\u1EC1 Ch\xFAa C\u1EE9u Th\u1EBF trong \u0111\u1EDDi n\u1EA7y m\xE0 th\xF4i th\xEC ch\xFAng ta l\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xE1ng th\u01B0\u01A1ng nh\u1EA5t trong t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi s\u1ED1ng tr\xEAn th\u1EBF gian. "), mdx("h6", {
