    "id": "v26"
  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "K\u1EBB th\xF9 b\u1ECB ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng l\xE0 s\u1EF1 ch\u1EBFt. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v27"
  }, "v27"), mdx("p", null, "Th\xE1nh Kinh ch\xE9p r\u1EB1ng Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF s\u1EBD \u0111\u1EB7t h\u1EBFt m\u1ECDi v\u1EADt d\u01B0\u1EDBi quy\u1EC1n cai tr\u1ECB c\u1EE7a Ng\xE0i. Khi Th\xE1nh Kinh vi\u1EBFt \"m\u1ECDi v\u1EADt\" d\u01B0\u1EDBi quy\u1EC1n Ng\xE0i th\xEC \u0111i\u1EC1u \u1EA5y kh\xF4ng c\xF3 ngh\u0129a l\xE0 k\u1EC3 lu\xF4n Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF, \u0110\u1EA5ng \u0111\u1EB7t m\u1ECDi v\u1EADt d\u01B0\u1EDBi quy\u1EC1n Ch\xFAa C\u1EE9u Th\u1EBF. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v28"
  }, "v28"), mdx("p", null, "Sau khi m\u1ECDi v\u1EADt \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c \u0111\u1EB7t d\u01B0\u1EDBi quy\u1EC1n m\xECnh xong th\xEC \u0110\u1EE9c Ch\xFAa Con c\u0169ng s\u1EBD t\u1EF1 \u0111\u1EB7t m\xECnh d\u01B0\u1EDBi quy\u1EC1n Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF l\xE0 \u0110\u1EA5ng \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1EB7t m\u1ECDi s\u1EF1 d\u01B0\u1EDBi quy\u1EC1n m\xECnh. B\u1EA5y gi\u1EDD Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF s\u1EBD ho\xE0n to\xE0n qu\u1EA3n tr\u1ECB m\u1ECDi lo\xE0i. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v29"
  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "N\u1EBFu k\u1EBB ch\u1EBFt kh\xF4ng s\u1ED1ng l\u1EA1i th\xEC t\u1EA1i sao ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta ch\u1ECBu ph\xE9p b\xE1p-t\xEAm v\xEC nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u1EBFt? N\u1EBFu k\u1EBB ch\u1EBFt kh\xF4ng s\u1ED1ng l\u1EA1i th\xEC ch\u1ECBu ph\xE9p b\xE1p-t\xEAm v\xEC h\u1ECD \u0111\u1EC3 l\xE0m g\xEC? "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v30"
  }, "v30"), mdx("p", null, "C\xF2n ch\xFAng t\xF4i th\xEC sao? T\u1EA1i sao ch\xFAng t\xF4i l\u1EA1i t\u1EF1 \u0111\u01B0a m\xECnh v\xE0o ch\u1ED1n hi\u1EC3m nguy m\u1ED7i gi\u1EDD? "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v31"
  }, "v31"), mdx("p", null, "T\xF4i ch\u1EBFt m\u1ED7i ng\xE0y. Th\u01B0a anh ch\u1ECB em, \u0111i\u1EC1u \u1EA5y qu\u1EA3 \u0111\xFAng nh\u01B0 th\u1EBF c\u0169ng nh\u01B0 \u0111i\u1EC1u t\xF4i khoe v\u1EC1 anh ch\u1ECB em trong Ch\xFAa C\u1EE9u Th\u1EBF Gi\xEA-xu ch\xFAng ta c\u0169ng \u0111\xFAng n\u1EEFa. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v32"
  }, "v32"), mdx("p", null, "N\u1EBFu t\xF4i suy ngh\u0129 theo con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi m\xE0 chi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EA5u v\u1EDBi d\xE3 th\xFA \u1EDF th\xE0nh \xCA-ph\xEA-s\xF4 th\xEC c\xF3 \xEDch g\xEC \u0111\xE2u? N\u1EBFu k\u1EBB ch\u1EBFt kh\xF4ng s\u1ED1ng l\u1EA1i th\xEC \"Ch\xFAng ta h\xE3y \u0103n, u\u1ED1ng cho th\u1ECFa th\xEDch v\xEC ng\xE0y mai ch\xFAng ta \u0111\u1EC1u ch\u1EBFt h\u1EBFt.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v33"
  }, "v33"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110\u1EEBng m\u1EAFc l\u1EEBa, \"B\u1EA1n x\u1EA5u l\xE0m h\u01B0 t\xEDnh t\u1ED1t.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v34"
  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "H\xE3y tr\u1EDF l\u1EA1i l\u1ED1i suy ngh\u0129 ch\xEDnh \u0111\xE1ng c\u1EE7a anh ch\u1ECB em v\xE0 \u0111\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1m t\u1ED9i n\u1EEFa. M\u1ED9t v\xE0i ng\u01B0\u1EDDi trong anh ch\u1ECB em kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF l\xE0 g\xEC--t\xF4i n\xF3i th\u1EBF \u0111\u1EC3 anh ch\u1ECB em t\u1EF1 th\u1EB9n.Ch\xFAng ta s\u1EBD mang th\xE2n x\xE1c n\xE0o? "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v35"
  }, "v35"), mdx("p", null, "Tuy nhi\xEAn c\xF3 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi s\u1EBD h\u1ECFi, \"Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u1EBFt s\u1ED1ng l\u1EA1i ra sao? H\u1ECD s\u1EBD mang th\xE2n x\xE1c n\xE0o?\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v36"
  }, "v36"), mdx("p", null, "K\u1EBB d\u1EA1i \u01A1i! Khi gieo h\u1ED9t gi\u1ED1ng th\xEC h\u1ED9t \u1EA5y ph\u1EA3i ch\u1EBFt d\u01B0\u1EDBi l\xF2ng \u0111\u1EA5t tr\u01B0\u1EDBc r\u1ED3i m\u1EDBi s\u1ED1ng l\u1EA1i v\xE0 m\u1ECDc l\xEAn. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v37"
  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "Khi gieo h\u1ED9t th\xEC h\xECnh th\u1EC3 c\u1EE7a n\xF3 kh\xE1c v\u1EDBi h\xECnh th\u1EC3 sau n\u1EA7y. H\u1ED9t gi\u1ED1ng anh ch\u1ECB em gieo c\xF3 th\u1EC3 ch\u1EC9 l\xE0 m\u1ED9t h\u1ED9t th\u01B0\u1EDDng, l\xFAa m\xEC hay b\u1EA5t c\u1EE9 h\u1ED9t g\xEC. "), mdx("h6", {
